p: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>E</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>M</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>A</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>S</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\"><strong>_</strong></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border: solid black 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">15</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">29</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">4</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">5</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">29</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">19</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">9</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">19</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">20</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">5</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">13</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">1</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">19</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.45pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: solid black 1.0pt; border-right: solid black 1.0pt; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; line-height: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">29</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Como a matriz codificadora (matriz A) tem duas linhas e duas colunas, &eacute; preciso arranjar a sequ&ecirc;ncia de n&uacute;meros em uma matriz com duas linhas. Assim, a matriz mensagem (M) ser&aacute;:</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">M = [4 &nbsp;5 &nbsp;19 &nbsp;5&nbsp; 14&nbsp; 22&nbsp; 15&nbsp; 12&nbsp; 22&nbsp; 9&nbsp; 13&nbsp; 5&nbsp; 14 20</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 15&nbsp; 29&nbsp; 4&nbsp; 5&nbsp; 29&nbsp; 19&nbsp; 9&nbsp; 19&nbsp; 20&nbsp; 5&nbsp; 13&nbsp; 1&nbsp; 19&nbsp; 29]</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Se a mensagem tivesse uma quantidade &iacute;mpar de s&iacute;mbolos, voc&ecirc; poderia acrescentar um espa&ccedil;o (_ - 29) ou um n&uacute;mero qualquer maior que 30, no final. Agora, para codificar a mensagem, multiplicamos a matriz M &agrave; esquerda pela matriz codificada A:</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">N = A x M</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">N = [5&nbsp; 7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; [4&nbsp; 5&nbsp; 19&nbsp; 5&nbsp; 14&nbsp; 22&nbsp; 15&nbsp; 12&nbsp; 22&nbsp; 9&nbsp; 13&nbsp; 5&nbsp; 14&nbsp; 20</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;X</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2&nbsp; 3]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 15&nbsp; 29&nbsp; 4&nbsp; 5&nbsp; 29&nbsp; 19&nbsp; 9&nbsp; 19&nbsp; 20&nbsp; 5&nbsp; 13&nbsp; 1&nbsp; 19&nbsp; 29]</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">N = [123&nbsp; 228&nbsp; 123&nbsp; 60&nbsp; 245&nbsp; 243&nbsp; 138&nbsp; 193&nbsp; 250&nbsp; 80&nbsp; 156&nbsp; 32&nbsp; 203&nbsp; 303</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;53&nbsp; 97&nbsp; 50&nbsp; 25&nbsp; 103&nbsp; 101&nbsp; 57&nbsp; 81&nbsp; 104&nbsp; 33&nbsp; 65&nbsp; 13&nbsp; 85&nbsp; 127]</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">E, em seguida, alinhamos os elementos de 𝑁 = 𝐴 &sdot; 𝑀 para formarmos a mensagem codificada. Utilizamos v&iacute;rgula entre os n&uacute;meros para facilitar a leitura na hora da decodifica&ccedil;&atilde;o.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">A mensagem codificada &eacute;: 123, 228, 123, 60, 245, 243, 138, 193, 250, 80, 156, 32, 203, 303, 53, 97, 50, 25, 103, 101, 57, 81, 104, 33, 65, 13, 85, 127;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Uma importante caracter&iacute;stica deste tipo de criptografia &eacute; que enquanto havia repeti&ccedil;&otilde;es representando letras repetidas na mensagem original, essas repeti&ccedil;&otilde;es n&atilde;o se preservam na mensagem codificada. Os decifradores de c&oacute;digos mais simples come&ccedil;am sempre pelas repeti&ccedil;&otilde;es. Aqui, estes decodificadores n&atilde;o t&ecirc;m por onde come&ccedil;ar.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Quando esta mensagem codificada chega, o destinat&aacute;rio realiza os passos contr&aacute;rios e a sua primeira a&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; transformar a sequ&ecirc;ncia num&eacute;rica em uma matriz N de duas linhas:</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">N = [123&nbsp; 228&nbsp; 123&nbsp; 60&nbsp; 245&nbsp; 243&nbsp; 138&nbsp; 193&nbsp; 250&nbsp; 80&nbsp; 156&nbsp; 32&nbsp; 203&nbsp; 303</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 53&nbsp; 97&nbsp; 50&nbsp; 25&nbsp; 103&nbsp; 101&nbsp; 57&nbsp; 81&nbsp; 104&nbsp; 33&nbsp; 65&nbsp; 13&nbsp; 85&nbsp; 127]</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Em seguida, ele utiliza a matriz decodificadora B para reverter os passos acima. Para tal, ele aplica a seguinte propriedade da multiplica&ccedil;&atilde;o de matrizes: 𝐵 x 𝑁 = 𝐵 x 𝐴 x 𝑀 = 𝐼 x 𝑀 = 𝑀</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">Portanto, se o decodificador usar a mensagem codificada para construir uma matriz com duas linhas e depois multiplicar esta matriz &agrave; esquerda por B, ele obter&aacute; a matriz M do remetente.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 107%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Calibri, sans